{
  "stem": "11290.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was one of the last people that could bring out an uninspected, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] uninspected lift, they called it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a package of furniture.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because later on, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] somebody had to come and inspect everything that a Jew wanted to take out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like, for instance, when the pieces of the furniture of my great grandparents-- the Biedermeier furniture that we wanted to bring-- my parents brought with them in 1938.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But at that time, they had to pay full price.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What they took out, which was their own property, was assessed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The value was assessed at very high prices.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they had to pay that before they could take it out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In other words, they had to rebuy everything that belonged to them already.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was not the case yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I brought only personal, personal, personal effects.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I came the United States.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The boat was already crowded with refugees.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was an American boat because I wanted to be in America as soon as possible.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I knew as soon I entered the American ship in Hamburg, I was in America, in a way.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Also, at that time, Ellis Island still existed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I didn't know, but everything went very smooth with the exception-- I mean, it was-- On the boat, we had-- first of all, we met many people who came from small cities, smaller towns in Germany who had gone through already at that time through beatings, murder.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And their experience has been much worse than that in the big-- in the big cities because nobody checked on it.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
